Change log of kd-tree library
=============================

Version 1.2 from 2022-10-17
---------------------------

 - search functions k_nearest_neighbors and range_nearest_neighbors are
   now thread safe, i.e., they can be called serveral times in parallel

 - new property KdNode::index for optionally storing the point index

 - exception thrown if vector nodes empty in constructor of KdTree


Version 1.1 from 2020-12-02
---------------------------

 - removed "unused argument" warning of some compilers


Version 1.0 from 2019-02-11
---------------------------

 - first release under BSD license

